  "body": "If we repeatedly fail to retrieve the conversion rates for a specific token, we should provide the option of clearing the stale rates. This would let us ensure that users are not misled by the stale value. It should be optional to simplify the process of rolling this out across mobile and extension.\r\n\r\nThe time to wait before considering a rate as \"stale\" should be configurable.",
